    "used rule-based systems and the BART (Bidirectional and Auto-Regressive Transformer) model 26 for this purpose and demonstrated convincing results.",
    "However, BART-generated content was less favored by human experts more than 50% of the time, perhaps due to the smaller number of parameters than current state-of-the-art LLMs 26.",
    "The application of billion-parameter LLMs to generate echo reports remains under-explored 27, 28.",
    "In this work, we proposed to construct a local, domain-specific LLM (EchoGPT) dedicated to echocardiography report summarization through an instruction fine-tuning approach, which is known to be an effective strategy to adapt LLMs for similar tasks 13, 18.",
